About Me

I am a Data Scientist and Geologist currently interning at Unify Consulting. My skill set includes technical writing, computer programming, and statistics with a focus on business intelligence. I have previously worked modeling slope stability hazards and writing detailed geotechnical reports. My career goals include gaining technical data science experience while completing a related graduate program. I hope to build a career analyzing and mining data to drive informed business decisions.
